{"tid":607103,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"中國政府修例，燒咗本特區護照佢啦。","createTime":"2018-03-27T04:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T18:31:30.000Z","uid":53416,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e13e0d713e00acbd6b9e5224572e4fd799da153b","tid":607103,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&d=1i6%2BM0Kai%2BovlyjlPb85JTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=85736ae2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&h=3452592b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n中國疑修例，不再向勸阻不聽還去危險國家的公民提供免費領事保護服務。聽落好似唔關你事？咁你就錯啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁出現問題啦，香港特别行政區護照持有人係由中國使領館提供領事保護，香港本身無提供，亦無權提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府本身亦無就外交部發出的外遊警告作出特別通報，香港本身就只有自己一套嘅外遊警示系統。香港居民唔會，亦無必要閱讀中國外交部的公告，相反外交部亦不會通報香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n再說，中國法律在香港沒有效力。但若果有關法例影響到香港居民在外的合法領事保護權，即等同中國單方面將法律在香港實行。<br />\n<br />\n咁就出現幾個問題啦。<br />\n<br />\n1. 有關法令會否影響香港特區護照持有人的領事保護權利?<br />\n2. 有關法例是否亦適於於香港特區護照持有人?<br />\n3. 當外交部與香港外遊警示系統出現不一致的情況下，香港人何去何從?<br />\n4. 你估個個外遊都係去玩嘅咩，因公出行的領事服務是否受到影響?<br />\n5. 最重要的是：這是否違反基本法的行為?<br />\n<br />\n個重點就係：若果有關法律在中國獲得通過的話，特區護照燒咗佢啦，用BNO好過。"},{"pid":"0113efc1a3c0b980245df3622363461189710107","tid":607103,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&d=1i6%2BM0Kai%2BovlyjlPb85JTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=85736ae2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&h=3452592b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447</a>"},{"pid":"902d832f3cd31f372a7b34a0d0a1ea0e9461f668","tid":607103,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"中國疑修例，不再向勸阻不聽還去危險國家的公民提供免費領事保護服務<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b513db1b09b0c1bc0bb86dcb2c888f9639b3bc","tid":607103,"uid":36157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"全世界都危險，只有中囯安全喎好似係。"},{"pid":"dee2b8003a541386c052d80d2a8f68a316eaae7c","tid":607103,"uid":32588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"根本危唔危險都無領事保護服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd8259aec0cb373d3d9b19996dc94408b5b40d4","tid":607103,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b513db1b09b0c1bc0bb86dcb2c888f9639b3bc","tid":607103,"uid":36157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"全世界都危險，只有中囯安全喎好似係。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"爱国爱党<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32c672220a3499769d2d08a13ccb54ae6f8baed","tid":607103,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dee2b8003a541386c052d80d2a8f68a316eaae7c","tid":607103,"uid":32588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"根本危唔危險都無領事保護服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3add6b50e00a252bb6d114575cd87c2a269fb27e","tid":607103,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"吳京又話幾危險都嚟救嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3af16c4097cf0e8fd41e59c64